#. BVbtH
#: 03050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150249\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Decreases the display scale of formulas by 25%.</ahelp> The current zoom factor is displayed on the status bar. A selection of available zoom options is accessible through the <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000001.xhp#contextmenu\">context menu</link>. The context menu in the work area also contains zoom commands."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຫຼຸດຂະໜາດການສະແດງຜົນຂອງສູດລົງ 25%.</ahelp> ອັດຕາການຂະຫຍາຍປັດຈຸບັນຈະສະແດງຢູ່ໃນແຖບສະຖານະ. ຕົວເລືອກການຂະຫຍາຍຕ່າງໆ ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ຜ່ານ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000001.xhp#contextmenu\">ເມນູລັດ</link>. ເມນູລັດໃນພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກຍັງມີຄຳສັ່ງການຂະຫຍາຍນຳອີກ."

