"03090200.xhp\n"
"par_id3156000\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Type <emph>ll</emph> or <emph><<</emph> in the <emph>Commands</emph> window to insert the <emph>much less than</emph> relation into the formula."
msgstr "ພິມ <emph>ll</emph> ຫຼື <emph><<</emph> ໃນໜ້າຕ່າງ <emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph> ເພື່ອແຊກສາຍພົວພັນແບບ <emph>ນ້ອຍກວ່າຫຼາຍ</emph> ເຂົ້າໃນສູດ."

#. nxTab
