"03090700.xhp\n"
"par_id3147531\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_SMA_LSUPX\">Inserts a superscript to the left of a placeholder.</ahelp> You can also type <emph><?>lsup{<?>}</emph> in the <emph>Commands</emph> window."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_SMA_LSUPX\">ແຊກເລກກຳລັງໄວ້ທາງຊ້າຍຂອງຕົວແທນ.</ahelp> ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດພິມ <emph><?>lsup{<?>}</emph> ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph> ໄດ້."

