#. iggUG
#: 03090700.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03090700.xhp\n"
"par_id3159195\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_SMA_CSUPX\">Inserts a superscript directly above a placeholder.</ahelp> You can also type <emph><?>csup<?></emph> directly in the <emph>Commands</emph> window."
