msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_SMA_XINTERSECTIONY\">Use this icon to insert two placeholders with the set operator <emph>intersection of sets </emph>.</ahelp> The same happens if you enter <emph><?> intersection <?></emph> Commands window."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_SMA_XINTERSECTIONY\">ໃຊ້ໄອຄອນນີ້ເພື່ອແຊກສອງຕົວແທນພ້ອມກັບຕົວດຳເນີນການກຸ່ມ <emph>ອິນເຕີເຊັກຊັນຂອງກຸ່ມ</emph>.</ahelp> ສິ່ງດຽວກັນນີ້ຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນຖ້າທ່ານພິມ <emph><?> intersection <?></emph> ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ ຄຳສັ່ງ."

