#. B9j6D
#: 03091300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091300.xhp\n"
"par_id3150051\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Additional information about attributes in <emph>$[officename] Math</emph> is found here."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບຄຸນລັກສະນະໃນ <emph>$[officename] Math</emph> ສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ທີ່ນີ້."

#. hQVAN
#: 03091300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091300.xhp\n"
"par_id3146966\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>acute</emph>, <emph>bar</emph>, <emph>breve</emph>, <emph>check</emph>, <emph>circle</emph>, <emph>dot</emph>, <emph>ddot</emph>, <emph>dddot</emph>, <emph>grave</emph>, <emph>hat</emph>, <emph>tilde</emph> and <emph>vec</emph> attributes always have a fixed size and do not become wider (longer) if they are above a long symbol. By default, the attributes are centered."
msgstr "ຄຸນລັກສະນະ <emph>acute</emph>, <emph>bar</emph>, <emph>breve</emph>, <emph>check</emph>, <emph>circle</emph>, <emph>dot</emph>, <emph>ddot</emph>, <emph>dddot</emph>, <emph>grave</emph>, <emph>hat</emph>, <emph>tilde</emph> ແລະ <emph>vec</emph> ຈະມີຂະໜາດຄົງທີ່ສະເໝີ ແລະ ຈະບໍ່ກວ້າງຂຶ້ນ (ຍາວຂຶ້ນ) ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າມັນຈະຢູ່ເທິງສັນຍະລັກທີ່ຍາວກໍຕາມ. ໂດຍຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ຄຸນລັກສະນະເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກຈັດໄວ້ຢູ່ເຄິ່ງກາງ."

#. FZcGj
#: 03091300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091300.xhp\n"
"par_id3154557\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The only attributes which grow with the length of the symbol are <emph>overline</emph>, <emph>underline</emph> and <emph>overstrike</emph>."
msgstr "ຄຸນລັກສະນະພຽງແຕ່ຢ່າງດຽວທີ່ຈະຂະຫຍາຍຕາມຄວາມຍາວຂອງສັນຍະລັກແມ່ນ <emph>overline</emph> (ຂີດເທິງ), <emph>underline</emph> (ຂີດກ້ອງ) ແລະ <emph>overstrike</emph> (ຂີດທັບ)."

#. yno7Y
#: 03091300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091300.xhp\n"
"par_id3151180\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For some character strings, it is possible that a line inserted with <emph>underline</emph> is too close to the character. In this case, an empty group can solve the problem: <emph>underline Q sub {}</emph> instead of <emph>underline Q</emph>."
msgstr "ສຳລັບບາງຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ເປັນໄປໄດ້ວ່າເສັ້ນທີ່ແຊກດ້ວຍ <emph>underline</emph> ອາດຈະຢູ່ໃກ້ຕົວອັກສອນເກີນໄປ. ໃນກໍລະນີນີ້, ການໃຊ້ກຸ່ມວ່າງສາມາດຊ່ວຍແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາໄດ້: <emph>underline Q sub {}</emph> ແທນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ <emph>underline Q</emph>."

#. bXUnD
