msgstr "<link href=\"text/smath/01/03091400.xhp\">ການປັບຂະໜາດ</link>"

#. n356e
#: 03091400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091400.xhp\n"
"par_id3147173\n"
"help.text"
msgid "More detailed information about scaling in <emph><item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Math</emph> as well as some examples can be found here. (The quotation marks in this text are for emphasis purposes only and are not part of the examples.)"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບການປັບຂະໜາດໃນ <emph><item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Math</emph> ລວມທັງຕົວຢ່າງບາງຢ່າງສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ທີ່ນີ້. (ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມນີ້ແມ່ນເພື່ອເນັ້ນໜັກເທົ່ານັ້ນ ແລະ ບໍ່ໄດ້ເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຕົວຢ່າງ.)"

#. yva3E
#: 03091400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091400.xhp\n"
"par_id3156316\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The factorial is not scaled (example: \"fact stack{a#b}\" and \"fact {a over b}\") but is oriented using the baseline or center of the arguments."
msgstr "ຟັກໂຕຣຽວ (factorial) ຈະບໍ່ຖືກປັບຂະໜາດ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: \"fact stack{a#b}\" ແລະ \"fact {a over b}\") ແຕ່ຈະຖືກວາງທິດທາງໂດຍໃຊ້ເສັ້ນພື້ນຖານ ຫຼື ຈຸດກາງຂອງຕົວໂຕ້ແຍ້ງ."

#. rAv9p
#: 03091400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091400.xhp\n"
"par_id3150756\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Brackets always have a fixed size as well. This applies to all symbols that can be used as brackets. Compare \"(((a)))\", \"( stack{a#b#c})\", \"(a over b)\"."
msgstr "ວົງເລັບກໍມີຂະໜາດຄົງທີ່ສະເໝີເຊັ່ນກັນ. ສິ່ງນີ້ໃຊ້ກັບທຸກສັນຍະລັກທີ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ເປັນວົງເລັບໄດ້. ປຽບທຽບ \"(((a)))\", \"( stack{a#b#c})\", \"(a over b)\"."

#. dSTPY
#: 03091400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091400.xhp\n"
"par_id3147570\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Brackets preceded by \"left\" or \"right\", however, are always adjusted to the argument. See \"left(left(left(a right)right)right)\", \"left(stack{a#b#c}right)\", \"left(a over b right)\"."
msgstr "ແນວໃດກໍຕາມ, ວົງເລັບທີ່ນຳໜ້າດ້ວຍ \"left\" ຫຼື \"right\" ຈະຖືກປັບໃຫ້ເຂົ້າກັບຕົວໂຕ້ແຍ້ງສະເໝີ. ເບິ່ງ \"left(left(left(a right)right)right)\", \"left(stack{a#b#c}right)\", \"left(a over b right)\"."

#. FSUZi
#: 03091400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091400.xhp\n"
"par_id3145206\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some <link href=\"text/smath/01/03091300.xhp\">Attributes</link> have fixed sizes; do not change these if they are placed above a long symbol."
msgstr "ບາງ <link href=\"text/smath/01/03091300.xhp\">ຄຸນລັກສະນະ</link> ມີຂະໜາດຄົງທີ່; ຢ່າປ່ຽນແປງສິ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຖ້າພວກມັນຖືກວາງໄວ້ເທິງສັນຍະລັກທີ່ຍາວ."

#. UeRh7
#: 03091400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03091400.xhp\n"
"par_id3154694\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The spaces in the examples are required for the correct structure. You may not delete them when making entries in the Commands window."
msgstr "ການເວັ້ນວ່າງໃນຕົວຢ່າງແມ່ນມີຄວາມຈຳເປັນເພື່ອໃຫ້ໄດ້ໂຄງສ້າງທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ທ່ານບໍ່ຄວນລຶບພວກມັນອອກເມື່ອປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຄຳສັ່ງ."

