#. D44KW
#: 05020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150213\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"schriftgroessentext\"><ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/fontsizedialog/FontSizeDialog\">Use this dialog to specify the font sizes for your formula. Select a base size and all elements of the formula will be scaled in relation to this base.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"schriftgroessentext\"><ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/fontsizedialog/FontSizeDialog\">ໃຊ້ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້ເພື່ອລະບຸຂະໜາດຕົວອັກສອນສຳລັບສູດຂອງທ່ານ. ເມື່ອເລືອກຂະໜາດພື້ນຖານແລ້ວ ທຸກອົງປະກອບຂອງສູດຈະຖືກປັບຂະໜາດຕາມອັດຕາສ່ວນຂອງພື້ນຖານນີ້.</ahelp></variable>"

#. GrnLV
#: 05020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146968\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Base size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດພື້ນຖານ"

#. UGSxe
#: 05020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3145115\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/fontsizedialog/spinB_baseSize\">All elements of a formula are proportionally scaled to the base size. To change the base size, select or type in the desired point (pt) size. You can also use other units of measure or other <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000003.xhp#measurement_units\">metrics</link>, which are then automatically converted to points.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/fontsizedialog/spinB_baseSize\">ທຸກອົງປະກອບຂອງສູດຈະຖືກປັບຂະໜາດຕາມອັດຕາສ່ວນຂອງຂະໜາດພື້ນຖານ. ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຂະໜາດພື້ນຖານ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ ຫຼື ພິມຂະໜາດພອຍ (pt) ທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ຫົວໜ່ວຍວັດແທກອື່ນໆ ຫຼື <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000003.xhp#measurement_units\">ມາດຕາວັດແທກ</link> ອື່ນໆ, ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກປ່ຽນເປັນພອຍໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ.</ahelp>"

#. qX3wh
#: 05020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153005\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To permanently change the default size (12 pt) used in $[officename] Math, you must first set the size (for example, 11 pt) and then click the <emph>Default</emph> button."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຂະໜາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ (12 pt) ທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນ $[officename] Math ແບບຖາວອນ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງຕັ້ງຂະໜາດກ່ອນ (ຕົວຢ່າງ 11 pt) ແລ້ວຈຶ່ງຄລິກປຸ່ມ <emph>ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ</emph>."

