msgstr "ປັບຂະໜາດວົງເລັບທັງໝົດ"

#. xCXkX
#: 05030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05030000.xhp\n"
"par_id3154799\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/spacingdialog/checkbutton\">Scales all types of brackets.</ahelp> If you then enter <emph>( a over b)</emph> in the <emph>Commands</emph> window, the brackets will surround the whole height of the argument. You normally achieve this effect by entering <emph>left ( a over b right )</emph>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/spacingdialog/checkbutton\">ປັບຂະໜາດວົງເລັບທຸກປະເພດ.</ahelp> ຫາກທ່ານພິມ <emph>( a over b)</emph> ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph>, ວົງເລັບຈະຫຸ້ມລວມຄວາມສູງທັງໝົດຂອງຕົວປ່ຽນ. ໂດຍປົກກະຕິແລ້ວ ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດແບບນີ້ໄດ້ດ້ວຍການພິມ <emph>left ( a over b right )</emph>."

#. ubo4x
#: 05030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05030000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151099\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Excess size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດສ່ວນເກີນ"

#. dnFBW
#: 05030000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05030000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147524\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Adjusts the percentage excess size.</ahelp> At 0 percent the brackets are set so that they surround the argument at the same height. The higher the entered value is, the larger the vertical gap between the contents of the brackets and the external border of the brackets. The field can only be used in combination with <emph>Scale all brackets</emph>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ປັບເປີເຊັນຂະໜາດສ່ວນເກີນ.</ahelp> ທີ່ 0 ເປີເຊັນ ວົງເລັບຈະຖືກຕັ້ງໃຫ້ຫຸ້ມຕົວປ່ຽນໃນຄວາມສູງດຽວກັນ. ຍິ່ງຄ່າທີ່ປ້ອນສູງຂຶ້ນ, ຊ່ອງວ່າງທາງຕັ້ງລະຫວ່າງເນື້ອໃນຂອງວົງເລັບ ແລະ ຂອບນອກຂອງວົງເລັບກໍຈະຍິ່ງກວ້າງຂຶ້ນ. ຫ້ອງນີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ກັບຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ປັບຂະໜາດວົງເລັບທັງໝົດ</emph> ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

