msgctxt ""
"05050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150206\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SID_TEXTMODE\">Switches the text mode on or off. In text mode, formulas are displayed as the same height as a line of text.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"SID_TEXTMODE\">ເປີດ ຫຼື ປິດໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ໃນໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ສູດຈະຖືກສະແດງໃຫ້ມີຄວາມສູງເທົ່າກັບແຖວຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ.</ahelp>"

