#. zFQGD
#: 06010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06010000.xhp\n"
"par_id3146313\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"symboletext\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Opens the <emph>Symbols</emph> dialog, in which you can select a symbol to insert in the formula.</ahelp> </variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"symboletext\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ສັນຍາລັກ</emph>, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກສັນຍາລັກເພື່ອແຊກເຂົ້າໃນສູດ.</ahelp> </variable>"

#. B7kGd
#: 06010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06010000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150202\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Symbol Set"
msgstr "ຊຸດສັນຍາລັກ"

#. 3zK7W
#: 06010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06010000.xhp\n"
"par_id3148699\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/catalogdialog/symbolset\">All symbols are organized into symbol sets. Select the desired symbol set from the list box. The corresponding group of symbols appear in the field below.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/catalogdialog/symbolset\">ສັນຍາລັກທັງໝົດຖືກຈັດເປັນຊຸດສັນຍາລັກ. ເລືອກຊຸດສັນຍາລັກທີ່ຕ້ອງການຈາກລາຍການ. ກຸ່ມສັນຍາລັກທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນໃນຫ້ອງດ້ານລຸ່ມ.</ahelp>"

#. S2tHq
#: 06010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06010000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153917\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When a symbol is selected, its command name appears below the symbol list and a magnified version appears in a box to the right. Note that the name must be typed in the <emph>Commands</emph> window exactly as displayed here (case-sensitive)."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເລືອກສັນຍາລັກໃດໜຶ່ງ, ຊື່ຄຳສັ່ງຂອງມັນຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນໃຕ້ລາຍການສັນຍາລັກ ແລະ ຮູບຂະຫຍາຍຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນໃນຫ້ອງທາງຂວາ. ໝາຍເຫດວ່າ ຊື່ຕ້ອງຖືກພິມໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph> ໃຫ້ຄືກັບທີ່ສະແດງຢູ່ນີ້ທຸກປະການ (ຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່ ແລະ ຕົວພິມນ້ອຍມີຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງກັນ)."

#. kNLCJ
#: 06010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06010000.xhp\n"
"par_id3149126\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To insert a symbol, select it from the list and click <emph>Insert</emph>. The corresponding command name appears in the <emph>Commands</emph> window."
msgstr "ເພື່ອແຊກສັນຍາລັກ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກມັນຈາກລາຍການ ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ແຊກ</emph>. ຊື່ຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph>."

#. 7EN3R
#: 06010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06010000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154765\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂ"

#. DFEpC
#: 06010000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06010000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153811\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/catalogdialog/edit\">Click here to open the <link href=\"text/smath/01/06010100.xhp\">Edit Symbols</link> dialog.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/smath/ui/catalogdialog/edit\">ຄລິກທີ່ນີ້ເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/smath/01/06010100.xhp\">ແກ້ໄຂສັນຍາລັກ</link>.</ahelp>"

#. dCQLd
