"06020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150251\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"formelimportierentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:ImportFormula\" visibility=\"visible\">This command opens a dialog for importing a formula.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"formelimportierentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:ImportFormula\" visibility=\"visible\">ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ຈະເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບສຳລັບການນຳເຂົ້າສູດ.</ahelp></variable>"

#. szJpE
#: 06020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153916\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Insert</emph> dialog is set up like the <link href=\"text/shared/01/01020000.xhp\"><emph>Open</emph></link> dialog under <emph>File</emph>. Use the <emph>Insert</emph> dialog to load, edit and display a formula saved as a file in the <emph>Commands</emph> window."
msgstr "ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ແຊກ</emph> ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າຄືກັບກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/shared/01/01020000.xhp\"><emph>ເປີດ</emph></link> ພາຍໃຕ້ເມນູ <emph>ໄຟລ໌</emph>. ໃຊ້ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ແຊກ</emph> ເພື່ອໂຫຼດ, ແກ້ໄຂ ແລະ ສະແດງສູດທີ່ບັນທຶກໄວ້ເປັນໄຟລ໌ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph>."

#. o4UTF
#: 06020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153917\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can import MathML files created by other applications as well. The MathML source must have a <item type=\"code\">math</item> element with an <item type=\"code\">xmlns</item> attribute with value \"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\". The languages MathML and StarMath are not fully compatible, therefore you should revise the import result. For details about the language MathML see its <link href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/#tr_MathML\">specification</link>."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດນຳເຂົ້າໄຟລ໌ MathML ທີ່ສ້າງໂດຍແອັບພລິເຄຊັນອື່ນໄດ້ອີກດ້ວຍ. ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ MathML ຕ້ອງມີອົງປະກອບ <item type=\"code\">math</item> ພ້ອມກັບຄຸນລັກສະນະ <item type=\"code\">xmlns</item> ທີ່ມີຄ່າເປັນ \"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\". ພາສາ MathML ແລະ StarMath ບໍ່ເຂົ້າກັນໄດ້ທັງໝົດ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນທ່ານຄວນກວດກາຜົນການນຳເຂົ້າຄືນໃໝ່. ສຳລັບລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບພາສາ MathML ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງທີ່ <link href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/#tr_MathML\">ຂໍ້ກຳນົດສະເພາະ</link> ຂອງມັນ."

#. LCQQn
#: 06020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06020000.xhp\n"
"bm_id3154661\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>MathML; import via clipboard</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>MathML; ນຳເຂົ້າຜ່ານຄລິບບອດ</bookmark_value>"

#. LDHGo
