#. cN3dZ
#: 06020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154661\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Import MathML from Clipboard"
msgstr "ນຳເຂົ້າ MathML ຈາກຄລິບບອດ"

#. AnBfM
#: 06020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150252\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"mathmlimportierentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:ImportMathMLClipboard\" visibility=\"visible\">This command transforms MathML clipboard content to StarMath and inserts it at the current cursor position.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"mathmlimportierentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:ImportMathMLClipboard\" visibility=\"visible\">ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ຈະປ່ຽນເນື້ອໃນ MathML ໃນຄລິບບອດໃຫ້ເປັນ StarMath ແລະ ແຊກມັນລົງໃນຕຳແໜ່ງເຄີເຊີປັດຈຸບັນ.</ahelp></variable>"

#. rU2Gi
#: 06020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153918\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the transformation fails, nothing is inserted."
msgstr "ຫາກການປ່ຽນແປງຂໍ້ມູນລົ້ມເຫຼວ, ຈະບໍ່ມີຫຍັງຖືກແຊກລົງໄປ."

#. xc4mE
#: 06020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153919\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This command handles only MathML content. If you have copied a %PRODUCTNAME Math formula to clipboard, insert it using the command <link href=\"text/shared/01/02060000.xhp\"><emph>Paste</emph></link> under <emph>Edit</emph>."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ຈັດການສະເພາະເນື້ອໃນ MathML ເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ຫາກທ່ານໄດ້ຄັດລອກສູດ %PRODUCTNAME Math ລົງໃນຄລິບບອດ, ໃຫ້ແຊກມັນໂດຍໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ <link href=\"text/shared/01/02060000.xhp\"><emph>ວາງ</emph></link> ພາຍໃຕ້ເມນູ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ</emph>."

